= *Allowed* Licenses

This page lists the all the licenses that are *allowed* for use in Fedora. If a
license is marked as *allowed*, it is allowed for any use. If a license is
marked as *allowed-fonts*, *allowed-content*, *allowed-documentation*, or
*allowed-firmware*, then it is allowed only for certain categories of material
as described in xref:license-approval.adoc[License Approval]. This information
is generated from data maintained in the
https://gitlab.com/fedora/legal/fedora-license-data[Fedora License Data]
repository. xref:allowed-licenses.adoc contains the same information, but
broken out to different tables for each category of *allowed*.

